title: Small youtuber looking to grow.

embed.description: Im baaaack --------------------- ► Never miss a video, subscribe here: ► http://bit.ly/1Rc7kzA ► Add me on Oceania! ► MrKillerKow ► Like my Facebook Page! ► https://www.facebook.com/MrKillerKow/ ► Song Used: ► Molly Moore - Imaginary Friends (TELYKast Remix) ► https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vo7NWIBMJS4 ► Outro Created By: ► KounterKurry ► https://goo.gl/7zKzAo

body: Hey, I'm a small youtuber that plans to upload every Saturday. I took a long break due to problems with my editing software and not much motivation, but from now on I plan to upload low elo montages and other random / funny videos like i used to at the start of the year. It would mean a lot to me if you could check out a video of mine and like. Feeling generous? Subscribing would make my day, hope you can enjoy my uploads! :)
